<exercise checkit-seed="0007" checkit-slug="P5" checkit-title="Expected Value">
    <statement>
        
                <p>
                    A resturant offers a grab bag of 24 fortune cookies, 4 of them have a discount of \$5 in them, 14 of them have a \$1 discount, and the rest have merely fortunes in them. If Kabir grabs one at random, what is the expected value of the draw?
                </p> 
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            The expected value is <me>\frac{4}{24}(5) + \frac{14}{24}(1) + 0 = $1.42</me>
        </p>
    </answer>
</exercise>
